data.description: Nearly new and perfect for you! Custom-built home in popular Bedico Creek is a dream come true. From the farmhouse-style vertical plank siding and bright red front door to the cypress-beam cathedral ceilings and lodge-style chandelier... every room shines with unique features and finishes. You'll love the plank wood floor, the sunlight streaming in from every window, and the open floor plan that flows effortlessly from cozy den to rustic dining to gourmet kitchen which puts HGTV to shame with its massive slab granite center island breakfast bar, black farmhouse sink with a slider window that opens to the side, handcrafted bead-board ceiling, drop-pendant lighting and upgraded professional stainless appliances including six-burner stove with restaurant-style range hood. Get ready to swoon over the owner's suite with spa-style full-wall shower for two (or more) and decadent slipper soaker tub. Spread out in spacious bedrooms (with great walk-in closet space), game room and flex spaces. Or head out to the backyard where you'll likely live on the screened-in lanai patio or around the sanctuary-style pool with a gas heater that gets up to 104 degrees overlooking the lake. Plus, a whole-house generator for peace of mind. No place like home never looked so beautiful!
